and border with India, requiring such bidders to be registered with the Competent Authority.', 'The successful completion of the contract will be determined by the fulfillment of the following conditions: The vendor must provide the Comprehensive Annual Maintenance Contract of Server and SAN Storage for the entire contract period of one year. All services must strictly meet the quality and technical specifications outlined in the referenced Bid document GEM/2025/B/6159599. The vendor''s performance must comply with the terms of the applicable Service Level Agreement for each service provided. The vendor must maintain compliance with GeM GTC clause 26 regarding bidders from countries sharing a land border with India, as any false declaration or non-compliance will be grounds for immediate termination of the contract and further legal action.', 'The scope of work involves providing a Comprehensive Annual Maintenance Contract of Server and SAN Storage at MS for a contract period of one year. The services must be delivered in accordance with the detailed technical specifications, terms, and conditions specified in the Bid document GEM/2025/B/6159599. The performance of these services will be governed by an applicable Service Level Agreement.'),
