on of the tendered work is contingent upon the following conditions: The vendor must complete the "Repair of Luff Slew Long Travel Main Hoist Motion and Auxiliary Hoist mot" within the stipulated 2-month contract period. The work must fully comply with the technical specifications, terms, and conditions detailed in the referenced Bid document GEM/2024/B/5748184. The services rendered must adhere to the applicable Service Level Agreement as provided in the Marketplace. Throughout the contract, the bidder must maintain compliance with GeM GTC clause 26 concerning bidders from countries sharing a land border with India, as any false declaration or non-compliance will be grounds for immediate termination of the contract.', 'The scope of work is for services related to the "Repair of Luff Slew Long Travel Main Hoist Motion and Auxiliary Hoist mot". Further detailed specifications, terms, and conditions are located in the referenced Bid document GEM/2024/B/5748184.'),
